ags:resource.dc:title: Results for the Atlantic cod, roughhead grenadier, redfish, thorny skate and black dogfish of the Spanish Survey in the NAFO Div. 3L for the period 2003-2013
ags:resource.dc:subject: Survey, Flemish Pass, Atlantic Cod, Roughhead grenadier, Redfish, Thorny skate, Black dogfish
ags:resource.dc:description: Since 2003, a stratified random spring bottom trawl survey was conducted by Spain in Division 3L of NAFO Regulatory Area (Flemish Pass). The surveys were carried out by the R/V “Vizconde de Eza” using bottom trawl net type Campelen. Entire series of mean catches, biomass and length distribution for Atlantic cod, roughhead grenadier, redfish, thorny skate and black dogfish are presented for the period 2003-2013.
ags:resource.dc:identifier: Consejo Científico de NAFO. (30/05/2014 - 12/06/2014. Halifax (Canadá)). 2014. NAFO SCR 14/016, Serial Number N6310
